				<li id="16528035" class="cmnt-root" data="21" data-d="1647517199000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t580158/Inseparable-Sword" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">17 Mar 2022 07:39</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16528035" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">TO GET THE SWORD:<br/>Step 1. Acquire the Twinned Armor set from killing D.<br/><br/>Step 2. Hand over the Twinned Armor set to D&apos;s Twin Brother in Siofra Aqueduct, Nokron, Eternal City.<br/><br/>Step 3. Complete Fia&apos;s Champion boss fight at Prince of Death&apos;s Throne, Deeproot Depths.<br/><br/>Step 4:<br/>- IF YOU FOLLOWED FIA&apos;S QUESTLINE + FOUGHT LICHDRAGON FORTISSAX: Acquire the Mending Rune of the Death-Prince from Fia&apos;s Body and rest at the grace. D&apos;s Twin Brother will spawn at Fia&apos;s body. After exhausting his dialogue, rest at the grace again and the Inseperable Sword should be on the ground.<br/>- IF YOU DID NOT FOLLOW FIA&apos;S QUESTLINE: (Not too sure about this path, but this is how I did it personally) Kill Fia and rest at the grace. The Inseperable Sword should be on the ground.<br/></p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16528035" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16528035" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon gly