				<li id="16518038" class="cmnt-root" data="135" data-d="1647423455000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t580158/Inseparable-Sword" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">16 Mar 2022 05:37</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16518038" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">Test-Anon here with a comparison between the three popular Faith Greatswords. I&apos;m comparing the Inseperable Sword, Golden Order Greatsword and Sacred Relic Sword witth each other and hope these numbers will help you form an informed decision on which weapon to use and upgrade according to your build. All tests were conducted with each weapon being at +10.<br/><br/>18 STR | 24 DEX | 28 FTH (Base Requirements met)<br/>Inseperable Sword 679 (+85 Holy Damage for 30 secs)<br/>Golden Order Greatsword 657<br/>Sacred Relic Sword 653 <br/>-------------------------<br/>18 STR | 24 DEX | 50 FTH<br/>Inseperable Sword 755  (+85 Holy Damage for 30 secs)<br/>Golden Order Greatsword 743<br/>Sacred Relic Sword 688<br/>-------------------------<br/>18 STR | 50 DEX | 28 FTH<br/>Inseperable Sword 717  (+85 Holy Damage for 30 secs)<br/>Golden Order Greatsword 694<br/>Sacred Relic Sword 748 <br/>-------------------------<br/>18 STR | 24 DEX | 80 FTH<br/>Inseperable Sword 794 (+85 Holy Damage for 30 secs)<br/>Golden Order Greatsword 786<br/>Sacred Relic Sword 706<br/><br/>Quick Facts:<br/>- Inseperable Greatsword and Golden Order Greatsword primarily benefit off of Faith, Sacred Relic Sword is DEX and STR is negligible<br/>- Inseperable Greatsword&apos;s 2-handed moveset uses the Hollowslayer&apos;s moveset <br/>- Ashe of War damage comparison: Golder Order Greatsword (requires both casts) &gt; Sacred Relic Sword &gt; Inseperable Sword<br/>- Inseperable Sword&apos;s Ashe of War does deal respectable damage, is the quickest to use and buffs the sword, making it overall my prefered weapon of the three to use</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16518038" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16518038" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">5</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>135</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>0</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16518038"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16518038" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16518038"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
